{
  "video_id": "p2NZGswoNO8",
  "title": "MLK on Guaranteed Income | Universal Basic Income (5 Reasons)",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 1180.0,
      "text": "At the end of his life..."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 1180.0,
      "end_time": 3900.0,
      "text": "Martin Luther King Jr. was working on a campaign..."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 3900.0,
      "end_time": 5520.0,
      "text": "...to ensure all Americans..."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 5520.0,
      "end_time": 8000.0,
      "text": "...had a dignified standard of living..."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 8000.0,
      "end_time": 10000.0,
      "text": "...with what is now referred to as a..."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 10000.0,
      "end_time": 12040.0,
      "text": "Universal Basic Income."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 12040.0,
      "end_time": 13620.0,
      "text": "Or as he called it:"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 13620.0,
      "end_time": 15760.0,
      "text": "A guaranteed minimum income..."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 15760.0,
      "end_time": 17660.0,
      "text": "...for all people..."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 17660.0,
      "end_time": 20620.0,
      "text": "...and all families of our country."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 31020.0,
      "end_time": 32920.0,
      "text": "The problems which are developing..."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 32920.0,
      "end_time": 35520.0,
      "text": "...as a result of automation and cybernation."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 35520.0,
      "end_time": 37800.0,
      "text": "As far back as 1961..."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 38020.0,
      "end_time": 40500.0,
      "text": "...MLK saw a new economic trend..."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 40500.0,
      "end_time": 42500.0,
      "text": "...of automation dissolving jobs\"."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 42500.0,
      "end_time": 44240.0,
      "text": "He called it a \"catastrophe\"..."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 44240.0,
      "end_time": 45480.0,
      "text": "...and said \"black and white...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 45480.0,
      "end_time": 46980.0,
      "text": "\"...we will all be harmed...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 46980.0,
      "end_time": 49780.0,
      "text": "\"...unless something grand and imaginative is done.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 49780.0,
      "end_time": 54000.0,
      "text": "\"A true revolution of values will soon look\nuneasily...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 54000.0,
      "end_time": 58400.0,
      "text": "\"...on the glaring contrast of poverty and wealth.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 58440.0,
      "end_time": 61140.0,
      "text": "\"It will look at thousands of working people...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 61140.0,
      "end_time": 64300.0,
      "text": "\"...displaced from their jobs with reduced income...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 64300.0,
      "end_time": 66440.0,
      "text": "...as a result of automation..."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 66440.0,
      "end_time": 70240.0,
      "text": "\"...while the profits of the employers remain intact...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 70240.0,
      "end_time": 72600.0,
      "text": "\"And say: \"This is not just.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 72600.0,
      "end_time": 75080.0,
      "text": "\"If a work program is impractical...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 75080.0,
      "end_time": 79080.0,
      "text": "\"...we are demanding a guaranteed income...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 79080.0,
      "end_time": 82880.0,
      "text": "\"...at levels that sustains life and decent circumstances.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 85900.0,
      "end_time": 89400.0,
      "text": "\"Poor black and white are still perishing...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 89400.0,
      "end_time": 91840.0,
      "text": "\"...on a lonely island of poverty...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 91840.0,
      "end_time": 95960.0,
      "text": "\"...in the midst of a vast ocean of material prosperity.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 95970.0,
      "end_time": 102360.0,
      "text": "MLK wrote he was convinced a guaranteed income\nwas \"the most effective\" solution to poverty."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 102360.0,
      "end_time": 105960.0,
      "text": "He argued past anti-poverty programs failed because..."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 105960.0,
      "end_time": 107200.0,
      "text": "They were \"sluggish\"...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 107200.0,
      "end_time": 108740.0,
      "text": "\"...entangled in bureaucracy...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 108740.0,
      "end_time": 109960.0,
      "text": "...and \"indirect\"."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 109960.0,
      "end_time": 113320.0,
      "text": "\"We are likely to find that the problem of\nhousing / education...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 113320.0,
      "end_time": 116600.0,
      "text": "\"...instead of preceding the elimination of poverty...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 116600.0,
      "end_time": 120240.0,
      "text": "\"...will themselves be effected if poverty is first abolished.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 120240.0,
      "end_time": 122900.0,
      "text": "\"The poor transformed into purchasers...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 122900.0,
      "end_time": 125240.0,
      "text": "\"...will do a great deal on their own...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 125240.0,
      "end_time": 127840.0,
      "text": "\"...to alter housing decay.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 130820.0,
      "end_time": 132200.0,
      "text": "Many people are worried..."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 132200.0,
      "end_time": 134200.0,
      "text": "...that if we had a guaranteed income..."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 134200.0,
      "end_time": 135840.0,
      "text": "...people would no longer work."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 135840.0,
      "end_time": 137500.0,
      "text": "But MLK disagreed."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 137500.0,
      "end_time": 139060.0,
      "text": "\"The fact is that...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 139060.0,
      "end_time": 141500.0,
      "text": "\"...the work which improves the condition of mankind...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 141500.0,
      "end_time": 143500.0,
      "text": "\"The work which extends knowledge\""
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 143500.0,
      "end_time": 144640.0,
      "text": "\"...and increases power...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 144640.0,
      "end_time": 145940.0,
      "text": "\"...and enriches literature...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 145940.0,
      "end_time": 147540.0,
      "text": "...\"and elevates thought...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 147540.0,
      "end_time": 149280.0,
      "text": "\"...is not done to secure a living.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 149280.0,
      "end_time": 151840.0,
      "text": "\"It is not the work of slaves, driven to their task...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 151840.0,
      "end_time": 155840.0,
      "text": "\"...either by a task master or by animal necessities.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 155840.0,
      "end_time": 157380.0,
      "text": "In a nutshell..."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 157380.0,
      "end_time": 158680.0,
      "text": "MLK argued..."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 158680.0,
      "end_time": 161120.0,
      "text": "...even if people didn't need a paycheck..."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 161120.0,
      "end_time": 163120.0,
      "text": "...they would still perform valuable work."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 163280.0,
      "end_time": 165720.0,
      "text": "Like working to raise the next generation."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 165720.0,
      "end_time": 167840.0,
      "text": "Working to improve oneself..."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 167840.0,
      "end_time": 170080.0,
      "text": "...or working to improve situations..."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 170080.0,
      "end_time": 171620.0,
      "text": "...and solve problems..."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 171620.0,
      "end_time": 172880.0,
      "text": "...that effect us all."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 172880.0,
      "end_time": 175680.0,
      "text": "\"In a state of society where want is abolished...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 175680.0,
      "end_time": 179200.0,
      "text": "\"...work of this sort could be enormously increased.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 183680.0,
      "end_time": 189360.0,
      "text": "\"A guaranteed income could be done for about $20 billion a year...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 189360.0,
      "end_time": 191680.0,
      "text": "And if our nation can spend..."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 191680.0,
      "end_time": 195840.0,
      "text": "$35 billion a year..."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 195840.0,
      "end_time": 198880.0,
      "text": "...to fight an unjust evil war in Vietnam..."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 198880.0,
      "end_time": 201040.0,
      "text": "...and $20 billion..."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 201040.0,
      "end_time": 202560.0,
      "text": "...to put a man on the moon..."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 202640.0,
      "end_time": 204880.0,
      "text": "...it can spend billions of dollars..."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 204880.0,
      "end_time": 207000.0,
      "text": "...to put God's children on their own two feet..."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 207020.0,
      "end_time": 208320.0,
      "text": "...right here on Earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 208320.0,
      "end_time": 215020.0,
      "text": "We are arrogant in professing to be concerned about the freedom of foreign nations..."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 215020.0,
      "end_time": 218960.0,
      "text": "...while not setting our own house in order."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 226880.0,
      "end_time": 229830.0,
      "text": "America is celebrated as the \"land of liberty\"."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 229840.0,
      "end_time": 231200.0,
      "text": "But MLK argued..."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 231200.0,
      "end_time": 235360.0,
      "text": "...if you have no income, you have no liberty."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 235680.0,
      "end_time": 237440.0,
      "text": "\"We read one day,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 237440.0,
      "end_time": 240000.0,
      "text": "\"We hold these truths to be self evident:\""
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 240000.0,
      "end_time": 241920.0,
      "text": "\"That all men are created equal...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 241920.0,
      "end_time": 246160.0,
      "text": "\"...that they are endowed by their creator\nwith certain inalienable rights...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 246160.0,
      "end_time": 247440.0,
      "text": "\"...that among these are...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 247440.0,
      "end_time": 249440.0,
      "text": "\"...life liberty, and the pursuit of\nhappiness.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 249920.0,
      "end_time": 254080.0,
      "text": "But if a man doesn't have a job or an income,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 254080.0,
      "end_time": 257660.0,
      "text": "...he has neither life..."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 257660.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260480.00000000003,
      "text": "...nor liberty..."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 260480.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263780.0,
      "text": "...[nor] the possibility for the pursuit of happiness.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 263780.0,
      "end_time": 265520.0,
      "text": "\"He merely exists.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 265520.0,
      "end_time": 268840.0,
      "text": "\"Now one of the answers it seems to me...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 268840.0,
      "end_time": 271760.0,
      "text": "...is a guaranteed annual income."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 271760.0,
      "end_time": 274280.0,
      "text": "...a guaranteed minimum income..."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 274280.0,
      "end_time": 275920.0,
      "text": "\"...for all people...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 275920.0,
      "end_time": 277960.0,
      "text": "\"...and for all families...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 277960.0,
      "end_time": 279960.0,
      "text": "\"...of our country.\""
    }
  ]
}